gobblin.util.recordcount

Class CompactionRecordCountProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • gobblin.util.RecordCountProvider
      • gobblin.util.recordcount.CompactionRecordCountProvider

  • public class CompactionRecordCountProvider
extends gobblin.util.RecordCountProvider
    Implementation of RecordCountProvider, which provides record count from file path. The file name should follow the pattern: {Prefix}{RecordCount}.{SystemCurrentTimeInMills}.{RandomInteger}{SUFFIX}. The prefix should be either M_OUTPUT_FILE_PREFIX or MR_OUTPUT_FILE_PREFIX. For example, given a file path: "/a/b/c/part-m-123.1444437036.12345.avro", the record count will be 123.
